bhop_kairos

This map is a port from my cs:go bhop map: https://gamebanana.com/maps/206603
For additional information about the map, please check that page.

This port was done by myself.

Small change in the skybox part of the map (in the green part). Different skybox was used, different concrete textures and different grass displacement textures (all visual). This shouldn't impact gameplay in any way.

Port was tested on CS:S without bhop settings enabled. All triggers are tested and are working, if you see any issue related to the port, please post them here.
